{{related|Datatypes-type}}
{{Identical|Lexeme}}

wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-intro:
A short text at the top of the page that allows users to merge two lexemes, explaining the form.

Followed by the following input box labels:
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-from-id}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-to-id}} 

This supports Wikitext.

wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-submit:
Label for the button that activates the action.

Preceded by the following input box labels:
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-from-id}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-lexeme-mergelexemes-to-id}}

wikibase-lexeme-summary-remove-form-gram:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when removing grammatical features. Example of a full edit summary is "Removed grammatical feature of lexicographical Form L1-F2: [[Item:Q123]]".}}

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of grammatical features removed.
* $2 - empty.
* $3 - lexicographical Form ID

{{Related|Wikibase-entity-summary}}

wikibase-lexeme-summary-remove-form-repr:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when removing lexicographical Form representations. Example of a full edit summary is "Removed representation of lexicographical Form L1-F2: en-us: color".}}

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of representations removed.
* $2 - empty.
* $3 - lexicographical Form ID.

{{Related|Wikibase-entity-summary}}

wikibase-lexeme-summary-set-form-represe:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when changing lexicographical Form representations. Example of a full edit summary is "Changed representation of lexicographical Form L1-F2: en-us: color".}}

Parameters:
* $1 - Number of representations changed.
* $2 - empty.
* $3 - lexicographical Form ID.

{{Related|Wikibase-entity-summary}}

wikibase-lexeme-summary-update-form-elem:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when changing multiple representations and grammatical features. Example of a full edit summary is "Changed representations and/or grammatical features of lexicographical Form L1-F2".}}

Parameters:
* $3 - lexicographical Form ID.

{{Identical|wikibase-lexeme-summary-update-form-elements}}
{{Related|Wikibase-entity-summary}}

wikibase-lexeme-summary-update-sense-ele:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when changing multiple glosses of a Sense.}}

Parameters:
* $3 is the sense ID.

wikibase-lexeme-summary-update-sense-glo:
{{wikibase summary messages|lexeme|Automatic edit summary generated when changing multiple glosses of a Sense.}}

Parameters:
* $3 is the sense ID.

wikibaselexeme-deletedentity-form:
