wikibaselexeme-deletedentity-lexeme:
Message displayed instead of a Lemma of the Lexeme if the Lexeme has been deleted.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-entity-item}}
* {{msg-mw|Wikibase-deletedentity-property}}

wikibaselexeme-deletedentity-sense:
Message displayed instead of a Sense's Gloss and Lemmas of the associated Lexeme if the Sense has been deleted.

See also:
